{"article_id":"KZLrxCFuHUArxnFp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The fate of the controversial Keystone pipeline is n't the only thing at stake during a crucial vote in the Senate on Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"A vote","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to move forward on legislation","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"approving the pipeline 's construction","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"would usher in a new era of animosity between resurgent Republicans in Congress and President Barack Obama .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"It could also determine the fate of embattled Democratic Sen. Mary Landrieu of Louisiana ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who is pushing the legislation in an uphill battle","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to fend off a GOP challenger in a runoff election next month .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Landrieu is very close to securing the support","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"necessary","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"to advance the legislation .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"All 45 Republicans will vote for the measure","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"and 14 Democrats are on record","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"supporting her .","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"But she needs one more Democrat","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"to join her","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"to reach the critical 60 vote threshold .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"By Monday night ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"she said","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"she had the votes necessary","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"It 's not clear whether she actually won someone over","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"or was just expressing confidence ahead of a vote","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that could determine her political future .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"In a three hour-long Senate floor debate Tuesday in advance of the vote , Landrieu was a bit more tentative .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"`` This is one of the first debates in eight years","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"where the outcome is uncertain , ''","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"`` We usually know the outcome of the vote","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"before we take it","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"because the deals are all cut . ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"In her speech , Landrieu made an aggressive case in favor","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"of approving the pipeline","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"while other Democrats dissented .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"`` To everyone","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"who thinks","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"this pipeline is the end of the world -- we already have 2.6 million miles of pipeline in the United States , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Landrieu said .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"`` We 're only completing basically 1,000 miles .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"What is everyone upset about ?","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"California Democratic Sen. Barbara Boxer pointed out the potential health risks","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"of laying the pipeline ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"including heart disease , increased hospitalization , and a higher prevalence of chemicals","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that `` penetrate deeply into the lungs . ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"`` The facts are the facts are the facts , ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"`` If you 're not a scientist","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"than be humble","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and listen to the peer-reviewed scientists .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"They do n't have a special interest .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"They have an interest","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"in giving us information","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"we should base our decisions upon. ``","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Boehner advises passage of Keystone","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Boehner advises passage of Keystone","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"00:34","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Boxer also referred to the project as the `` Keystone Extra Lethal Pipeline . ''","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"The GOP-led House on Friday approved a measure","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that will skip the conclusion of the six-year-old State Department review of the pipeline","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and authorize its construction .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"If the Senate ultimately approves the measure ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Obama could be poised to issue what would be just the third veto of his nearly six year presidency .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"At a news conference last week , Obama made clear","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that he does n't want Congress to interfere with the State Department 's process .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"`` Understand what this project is :","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"It is providing the ability of Canada","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"to pump their oil ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"send it through our land , down to the Gulf ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"where it will be sold everywhere else .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"It does n't have an impact on U.S. gas prices , ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Obama said at a Friday news conference in Myanmar .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"The showdown comes","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"as Obama and congressional Republicans appear to be on a collision course over immigration .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"Republicans are considering how to respond","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"if Obama follows through with a pledge","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"to revise immigration policies by the end of the year .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Some GOP lawmakers have talked about potentially shutting down the government","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"if Obama keeps that promise .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"On Keystone , Senate Democrats are moving toward a vote","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"largely to help Landrieu , the Senate Energy and Natural Resources chairwoman .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"She is facing off in the December runoff against Republican Rep. Bill Cassidy ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"who sponsored the House 's Keystone bill","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and has been promised a seat of his own on the energy panel .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"The measure offers Landrieu a final chance","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"to demonstrate her clout","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"before voters return to the polls .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Already , Landrieu was joined by 10 Democratic co-sponsors :","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Alaska Sen. Mark Begich , Arkansas Sen.","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Mark Pryor , Indiana Sen.","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Joe Donnelly , Missouri Sen.","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Claire McCaskill , Montana Sen.","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"Jon Tester , Montana Sen.","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"John Walsh , North Carolina Sen.","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"Kay Hagan , North Dakota Sen.","depth":17},{"id":97,"text":"Heidi Heitkamp , Virginia Sen.","depth":18},{"id":98,"text":"Mark Warner and West Virginia Sen. Joe Manchin .","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"Three more Democrats had pledged last week to support the measure :","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Colorado Sen. Michael Bennet , Delaware Sen. Tom Carper and Pennsylvania Sen. Bob Casey .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"The list of Landrieu 's potential Democratic allies","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to provide the final vote","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"is dwindling rapidly .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"One of Landrieu 's top targets , West Virginia Sen. Jay Rockefeller , said","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"he wo n't support the measure .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Another potential backer , Maine Sen. Angus King , an independent","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"who caucuses with the Democrats ,","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"told CNN Tuesday","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"he will vote against the bill","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Landrieu 's entreaties to other Democrats have also been rejected in recent days .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Outgoing Michigan Sen. Carl Levin wo n't support the pipeline ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"a spokeswoman said Monday .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Nor will New Jersey Sen. Cory Booker ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"who tweeted his opposition over the weekend .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Also confirming their opposition to the measure to various news outlets were Minnesota Sen. Amy Klobuchar , Florida Sen.","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Bill Nelson , New York Sen.","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Chuck Schumer , Delaware Sen.","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"Chris Coons , New Jersey Sen. Robert Menendez and Colorado Sen. Mark Udall .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"Retiring Democratic Sen. Tom Harkin of Iowa said","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"he would n't be voting for the pipeline .","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"`` I 've come to this conclusion :","depth":17},{"id":122,"text":"every dollar","depth":19},{"id":123,"text":"that we spend on fossil fuel development and use","depth":19},{"id":124,"text":"is another dollar","depth":19},{"id":125,"text":"we spend","depth":20},{"id":126,"text":"digging the graves of our grandchildren , ''","depth":20},{"id":127,"text":"he told reporters Tuesday .","depth":16},{"id":128,"text":"`` And I 'm not going to be a part of it anymore .","depth":17},{"id":129,"text":"I 'm through .","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"That 's just how strong I feel .","depth":16},{"id":131,"text":"I know","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"we ca n't solve it overnight ,","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"but we have to be on a steep glide path","depth":16},{"id":134,"text":"in getting rid of fossil fuels as a source of energy for our planet . ''","depth":16},{"id":135,"text":"Even Landrieu 's Democratic supporters were facing pressure .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Anti-Keystone activists ,","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"including college students ,","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"were trying Tuesday to convince Carper and Bennet to change their minds ,","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"protesting at the senators ' Capitol Hill offices .","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"`` We 've been playing politics for too long","depth":16},{"id":141,"text":"and this is not a political game ...","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"this is affecting everyone , ''","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"student Rachael Scheinman told CNN inside Bennet 's office ,","depth":16},{"id":144,"text":"holding a sign","depth":18},{"id":145,"text":"that read ,","depth":18},{"id":146,"text":"`` Sen. Bennet ,","depth":18},{"id":147,"text":"if you 're not a climate denier ,","depth":19},{"id":148,"text":"do n't vote like one . ''","depth":19},{"id":149,"text":"`` [ Bennet ] needs to vote his conscience on this one , ''","depth":16},{"id":150,"text":"added student Elli Bloomberg .","depth":16},{"id":151,"text":"The peaceful scene in Bennet 's office was in contrast to a more rambunctious protest in Carper 's office ,","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"where protestors loudly chanted ,","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"`` You ca n't eat money ,","depth":16},{"id":154,"text":"you ca n't drink oil , ''","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"`` Keep the tarsands in the soil ,","depth":17},{"id":156,"text":"we do n't want this dirty oil , ''","depth":17},{"id":157,"text":"and `` What do we want ? ''","depth":17},{"id":158,"text":"`` Climate justice , ''","depth":18},{"id":159,"text":"`` When do we want it ? '' `` Now . ''","depth":18},{"id":160,"text":"Staffers attempted to speak to protesters in Carper 's office and explain his vote .","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"`` What I hear you saying","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"is that the senator is politicizing an environmental crisis , ''","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"one protester said .","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"`` If he believes the science ,","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"there 's no reason","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"for him to be voting like this","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"and mortgaging our future , ''","depth":16},{"id":168,"text":"said another .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"Capitol police arrested four of the activists inside Carper 's office .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"They were escorted outside to chants of `` climate heroes . ''","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"Despite their intentions","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"to vote against the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"both Boxer and Senator Patrick Leahy","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"( D-Vt. )","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"congratulated Landrieu","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"for bringing the bill to the Senate floor in a move","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"Democrats hope","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"will rally votes in her favor in her upcoming runoff .","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"Senate approval of the Keystone pipeline is all but guaranteed ,","depth":5},{"id":181,"text":"with Republicans set","depth":6},{"id":182,"text":"to take control of the chamber in January .","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"The only question appears to be timing .","depth":4},{"id":184,"text":"As Landrieu and her allies search for Democratic support ,","depth":5},{"id":185,"text":"the pipeline is also becoming an issue in the 2016 campaign .","depth":5},{"id":186,"text":"New Jersey Gov . Chris Christie announced Monday","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"that he is planning a two-day swing through Canada in December .","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"That trip is expected to included an energy speech","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"that addresses the Keystone pipeline .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"`` My view is that we are missing an enormous opportunity","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"when we delay development of the Keystone XL pipeline , ''","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"Christie said in a speech during a recent trip to Mexico .","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"`` Not only is Keystone a major job creator ,","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"delays in its approval sends an unfortunate signal on multiple fronts . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":389,"left":0,"right":388,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":388,"left":373,"right":387,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":373,"left":267,"right":372,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":246,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":202,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":1,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":198,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":197,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":2,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":6,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":223,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":216,"right":222,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":213,"right":215,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":210,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":204,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":9,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":206,"right":208,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":12,"right":205,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":207,"right":17,"relation":